workouts.title: Neon Pulse
workouts.description: Push-ups 3 sets of reps until failure with 20-second rest in between sets. 3 sets of jumping jacks timed 45 seconds with 20-second breaks in between. Pull-ups until failure, 3 sets with 30-second rest between sets. 3 sets of squats until failure with 30-second breaks between each set.

workouts.title: Cyber Circuit
workouts.description: 5-minute brisk walk or jog. 3 sets of bodyweight squats, 10 reps each, with 15-second rest in between sets. 2 sets of planks, holding for 30 seconds, with 20-second rest in between sets.

workouts.title: Synthwave Sprint
workouts.description: High-intensity interval training (HIIT) circuit. 5 sets of burpees, 30 seconds on, 15 seconds off. 4 sets of mountain climbers, 45 seconds on, 20 seconds off. 3 sets of push-ups to failure with 25-second rest between sets. 4 sets of jumping lunges, 40 seconds on, 15 seconds off.

workouts.title: Galactic Grind
workouts.description: 3 sets of planks, holding for 45 seconds, with 20-second rest in between sets. 4 sets of Russian twists, 15 reps each side, with 15-second rest between sets. 3 sets of bicycle crunches, 20 reps each side, with 20-second rest between sets.

workouts.title: Vaporwave Vortex
workouts.description: 4 sets of squats, 12 reps each, with 30-second rest in between sets. 3 sets of lunges, 15 reps each leg, with 20-second rest between sets. 3 sets of calf raises, 20 reps each, with 25-second rest between sets.

workouts.title: Pixel Pumper
workouts.description: 5-minute brisk walk or jog. 2 sets of jumping jacks, 30 seconds each, with 15-second rest between sets. 2 sets of bodyweight squats, 12 reps each, with 20-second rest between sets.

workouts.title: Turbo Thrust
workouts.description: 4 sets of push-ups, 15 reps each, with 25-second rest between sets. 3 sets of dumbbell curls, 12 reps each arm, with 20-second rest between sets. 3 sets of tricep dips, 15 reps each, with 20-second rest between sets.

workouts.title: Retro Robustness
workouts.description: High-intensity interval training (HIIT) circuit. 5 sets of burpees, 30 seconds on, 15 seconds off. 4 sets of high knees, 45 seconds on, 20 seconds off. 3 sets of push-ups to failure with 25-second rest between sets. 4 sets of squat jumps, 40 seconds on, 15 seconds off.

workouts.title: Cassette Cardio
workouts.description: 10-minute yoga session focusing on flexibility and relaxation. Includes poses such as Downward Dog, Child's Pose, and Warrior II. Suitable for all fitness levels.

workouts.title: Core Burnout
workouts.description: 3 sets of planks, holding for 45 seconds, with 20-second rest in between sets. 4 sets of leg raises, 12 reps each, with 15-second rest between sets. 3 sets of bicycle crunches, 20 reps each side, with 20-second rest between sets.

workouts.title: 8-Bit Burn
workouts.description: 4 sets of squats, 12 reps each, with 30-second rest in between sets. 3 sets of step-ups, 15 reps each leg, with 20-second rest between sets. 3 sets of calf raises, 20 reps each, with 25-second rest between sets.

workouts.title: Future Fitness
workouts.description: 2 sets of planks, holding for 30 seconds, with 20-second rest in between sets. 3 sets of sit-ups, 15 reps each, with 15-second rest between sets. 2 sets of leg raises, 12 reps each, with 20-second rest between sets.

workouts.title: Retro Renegade
workouts.description: 5 sets of burpees, 30 seconds on, 15 seconds off. 4 sets of high knees, 45 seconds on, 20 seconds off. 3 sets of push-ups to failure with 25-second rest between sets. 4 sets of squat jumps, 40 seconds on, 15 seconds off.

workouts.title: Electro Blasters
workouts.description: 2 sets of push-ups, 10 reps each, with 25-second rest between sets. 3 sets of dumbbell curls, 12 reps each arm, with 20-second rest between sets. 3 sets of tricep dips, 15 reps each, with 20-second rest between sets.
